No. 08-1448. Edmund G. Brown, Jr., Governor of California, et al., Petitioners v. Entertainment Merchants Association, et al. 565 U.S. 809, 132 S. Ct. 81,

181 L. Ed. 2d 13,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6734. October 3, 2011.
